@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_clprpq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 1.00
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.92) * wp.exp(v2 + 0.41)) + (wp.abs(tmp + 0.48) * tmp))
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.40)) / ((tmp + 0.53 * v1 + 0.36) / v0))
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = 0.82
    data[tid] = v0
